### DevSpace API - Dynamic MongoDB Connection Examples
### Asegúrate de reemplazar las connection strings con las tuyas reales

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@mongoConnection = mongodb+srv://tu_usuario:tu_password@tu_cluster.mongodb.net/
@databaseName = tu_base_de_datos

### === FOLDERS ===

### Obtener todas las carpetas con conexión dinámica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear una nueva carpeta
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/folder
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Carpeta de Prueba",
  "parentFolderID": null
}

###

### Obtener carpeta por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Buscar carpetas por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder/search?name=prueba
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### === RESOURCES ===

### Obtener todos los recursos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear un nuevo recurso
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/resource
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Recurso de Prueba",
  "url": "https://github.com/",
  "description": "Un recurso de ejemplo para testing",
  "type": "URL",
  "folderId": null,
  "favorite": false
}

###

### Obtener recurso por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource/507f1f77bcf86cd799439012
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener recursos favoritos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource/favorites
X-MongoDB-Connection: {{mongoConnection}}
X-MongoDB-Database: {{databaseName}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### === TESTING CON CONEXIÓN POR DEFECTO ===

### Obtener carpetas sin headers dinámicos (usa conexión por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Obtener recursos sin headers dinámicos (usa conexión por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resource
Content-Type: application/json

###

### === TESTING DE ERRORES ===

### Intentar con connection string inválida
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder
X-MongoDB-Connection: invalid-connection-string
X-MongoDB-Database: test
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Intentar con connection string vacía
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/folder
X-MongoDB-Connection: 
X-MongoDB-Database: test
Content-Type: application/json

